Package: a2a-litestream
Version: 1.2.5
Architecture: all
Depends: litestream
Maintainer: A2A Team <team@greenhelix.net>
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Description: Litestream continuous replication for A2A SQLite databases
 Ships a litestream.yml config and systemd unit that stream every
 A2A product database (paywall, payments, gatekeeper, trust, etc.)
 to S3 with 5-minute snapshot cadence and 24-hour WAL retention.
 See /usr/share/doc/a2a-litestream/LITESTREAM_SETUP.md for the
 recovery runbook (RPO ~minute, RTO ~15 minutes).
